#: src/Weather/Rasp/RaspStore.cpp:29 src/Weather/Rasp/RaspStore.cpp:34
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Average dry thermal updraft strength near mid-BL height. Subtract glider "
"descent rate to get average vario reading for cloudless thermals. Updraft "
"strengths will be stronger than this forecast if convective clouds are "
"present, since cloud condensation adds buoyancy aloft (i.e. this neglects "
"\"cloudsuck\"). W* depends upon both the surface heating and the BL depth."
msgstr ""
"Prosek sešliščni tekmilski pohod v sredini visine BL. Odštejite spustajočo "
"hitrost letala, da dobite prosek četrtnečnikov mnenje za neoblačne termike. "
"Pohodna hitrost bo večja, če so prisotni konvektivni oblaki, ker se v nih "
"zvratno teče vzhod (tj. to zanemari \"oblakosuck\"). W* odvisni je od obeh "
"poverilnikov podnevanja in dubine BL."

#: src/Weather/Rasp/RaspStore.cpp:38
#, no-c-format
msgid "BL Wind spd"
msgstr "BL Vjeterni hitrost"

#: src/Weather/Rasp/RaspStore.cpp:39
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The speed and direction of the vector-averaged wind in the BL. This "
"prediction can be misleading if there is a large change in wind direction "
"through the BL."
msgstr ""
"Hitrost in smer vektorsko povprečenega vjetra v BL. Ta predviđanje lahko "
"zaviri, če postanejo velike spremembe v smeri vjetra skozi BL."

#: src/Weather/Rasp/RaspStore.cpp:43
#, no-c-format
msgid "H bl"
msgstr "H bl - V bl"

#: src/Weather/Rasp/RaspStore.cpp:44
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Height of the top of the mixing layer, which for thermal convection is the "
"average top of a dry thermal. Over flat terrain, maximum thermalling heights"
" will be lower due to the glider descent rate and other factors. In the "
"presence of clouds (which release additional buoyancy aloft, creating "
"\"cloudsuck\") the updraft top will be above this forecast, but the maximum "
"thermalling height will then be limited by the cloud base. Further, when the"
" mixing results from shear turbulence rather than thermal mixing this "
"parameter is not useful for glider flying."
msgstr ""
"Višina vrha smijevega sloja, ki je za termično konvekcijo povprečna vrh "
"sešliščnega tekmila. Na ravni terene bo maksimalna visina tekmiljanja manjša"
" zaradi spustajoče hitrosti letala in drugih faktorov. V prisotnosti oblakov"
" (ki vložijo dodatno zvratno tečnost vzhod, ustvarjujo \"oblakosuck\"), vrh "
"sešliščnega pohoda bo višji od toga predviđanja, vendar maksimalna visina "
"tekmiljanja bo omejena s podzemljem oblaka. Dopolnilno pa je, če je "
"smijevega sloja rezultat razmerje vzhodnega vjetra, ta parametar za letanje "
"sešlišča ni uporaben."

#: src/Weather/Rasp/RaspStore.cpp:48
#, no-c-format
msgid "dwcrit"
msgstr "dwcrit - dolžina kritične termike"

#: src/Weather/Rasp/RaspStore.cpp:49
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This parameter estimates the height above ground at which the average dry "
"updraft strength drops below 225 fpm and is expected to give better "
"quantitative numbers for the maximum cloudless thermalling height than the "
"BL Top height, especially when mixing results from vertical wind shear "
"rather than thermals. (Note: the present assumptions tend to underpredict "
"the max. thermalling height for dry conditions.) In the presence of clouds "
"the maximum thermalling height may instead be limited by the cloud base. "
"Being for \"dry\" thermals, this parameter omits the effect of "
"\"cloudsuck\"."
msgstr ""
"Ta parametar oceni višino nad zemljo, na kateri je prosek sešliščni pohod "
"manjši od 225 fpm in je očitnejše za kvantifikacijo maksimalne visine "
"tekmiljanja v neoblačnih termikih, kot je višina vrha BL. (Opomba: trenutna "
"predpostavka podcenjuje maksimalno visino tekmiljanja pri sešliščih brez "
"oblakov.) V prisotnosti oblakov bo maksimalna visina tekmiljanja omejena s "
"podzemljem oblaka. Za \"sešliščne\" termike ta parametar zanemari učinek "
"\"oblakosuck\"."

#: src/Weather/Rasp/RaspStore.cpp:53
#, no-c-format
msgid "bl cloud"
msgstr "bl oblaki"

#: src/Weather/Rasp/RaspStore.cpp:54
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This parameter provides an additional means of evaluating the formation of "
"clouds within the BL and might be used either in conjunction with or instead"
" of the other cloud prediction parameters. It assumes a very simple "
"relationship between cloud cover percentage and the maximum relative "
"humidity within the BL. The cloud base height is not predicted, but is "
"expected to be below the BL Top height."
msgstr ""
"Ta parametar ponuja dodatno način ocene formiranja oblakov v BL in se lahko "
"uporablja either splošne ali namreč kot alternativa drugim predviđanjem o "
"oblakih. Predpostavlja zelo preprosto odnos med procento pokritosti oblaka "
"in maksimalno relativno vlhkost v BL. Višina podzemlja oblaka ni predviđana,"
" ampak je očitna, da bo manjša kot višina vrha BL."

#: src/Weather/Rasp/RaspStore.cpp:58
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sfc temp"
msgstr "Površinska temperatura"

#: src/Weather/Rasp/RaspStore.cpp:59
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The temperature at a height of 2m above ground level. This can be compared "
"to observed surface temperatures as an indication of model simulation "
"accuracy; e.g. if observed surface temperatures are significantly below "
"those forecast, then soaring conditions will be poorer than forecast."
msgstr ""
"Temperatura na višini 2m nad površino. To se lahko primerja z pomerenimi "
"površinskimi temperaturemi kot oznako za točnost modelnega simulacije; npr.,"
" če so pomereni površinske temperature znatno nižje, od predviđanj, bodo "
"letanje kondicije slabše."

#: src/Weather/Rasp/RaspStore.cpp:63
#, no-c-format
msgid "hwcrit"
msgstr "hwcrit - višina kritične termike"

#: src/Weather/Rasp/RaspStore.cpp:64
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This parameter estimates the height at which the average dry updraft "
"strength drops below 225 fpm and is expected to give better quantitative "
"numbers for the maximum cloudless thermalling height than the BL Top height,"
" especially when mixing results from vertical wind shear rather than "
"thermals. (Note: the present assumptions tend to underpredict the max. "
"thermalling height for dry conditions.) In the presence of clouds the "
"maximum thermalling height may instead be limited by the cloud base. Being "
"for \"dry\" thermals, this parameter omits the effect of \"cloudsuck\"."
msgstr ""
"Ta parametar oceni višino, na kateri je prosek sešliščni pohod manjši od 225"
" fpm in je očitnejše za kvantifikacijo maksimalne visine tekmiljanja v "
"neoblačnih termikih, kot je višina vrha BL. (Opomba: trenutna predpostavka "
"podcenjuje maksimalno visino tekmiljanja pri sešliščih brez oblakov.) V "
"prisotnosti oblakov bo maksimalna visina tekmiljanja omejena s podzemljem "
"oblaka. Za \"sešliščne\" termike ta parametar zanemari učinek "
"\"oblakosuck\"."

#: src/Weather/Rasp/RaspStore.cpp:68
#, no-c-format
msgid "wblmaxmin"
msgstr "wblmaxmin - maksimalna/minimalna dolžina vleka"

#: src/Weather/Rasp/RaspStore.cpp:69
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Maximum grid-area-averaged extensive upward or downward motion within the BL"
" as created by horizontal wind convergence. Positive convergence is "
"associated with local small-scale convergence lines. Negative convergence "
"(divergence) produces subsiding vertical motion, creating low-level "
"inversions which limit thermalling heights."
msgstr ""
"Maksimalno mrežno povprečno intenzivno hrbtno ali padajoče potezo v BL, ki "
"jo ustvarijo horizontalne konvergenčne vjetri. Pozitivna konvergencija je "
"povezana z lokalnimi malimi konvergenčnimi linijami. Negativna konvergencija"
" (divergencija) ustvari padajoče vertikalno potezo, ki ustvarja dolge "
"inverze, omejujejoče tekmilne višine."

#: src/Weather/Rasp/RaspStore.cpp:73
#, no-c-format
msgid "blcwbase"
msgstr "podlagna osnovica"

