"Pravi bearing do naslednje obratne točke. ZA AAT naloge je to pravi bearing "
"do tarčne točke v območju AAT sektorja."

#: src/InfoBoxes/Content/Factory.cpp:151
#, no-c-format
msgid "GR instantaneous"
msgstr "Trenutna finesa"

#: src/InfoBoxes/Content/Factory.cpp:152
#, no-c-format
msgid "GR Inst"
msgstr "Finesa tr"

#: src/InfoBoxes/Content/Factory.cpp:153
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Instantaneous glide ratio over ground, given by the ground speed divided by "
"the vertical speed (GPS speed) over the last 20 seconds. Negative values "
"indicate climbing cruise. If the vertical speed is close to zero, the "
"displayed value is '---'."
msgstr ""
"Trenutno drsno razmerje (finesa), izračunana iz hitrosti, glede na tla "
"deljene z vertikalno hitrostjo (GPS hitrost) v zadnjih 20ih sekundah. "
"Negativne vrednosti pomenijo vzpenjanje med ravnim letom. Če je vertikalna "
"hitrost blizu 0, je prikazana vrednost '---'."

#: src/InfoBoxes/Content/Factory.cpp:159
#, no-c-format
msgid "GR cruise"
msgstr "Finesa križarjenje"

#: src/InfoBoxes/Content/Factory.cpp:160
#, no-c-format
msgid "GR Cruise"
msgstr "GR križarjenje"

#: src/InfoBoxes/Content/Factory.cpp:161
#, no-c-format
