#, no-c-format
msgid "WP ETE"
msgstr "Točka poti ETE"

#: src/InfoBoxes/Content/Factory.cpp:464
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Estimated time required to reach next waypoint, assuming performance of "
"ideal MacCready cruise/climb cycle."
msgstr ""
"Ocena časovnega potrebnega do naslednjega točke, predpostavljeno idealno "
"MacCready ciklus leta/poniščevanja."

#: src/InfoBoxes/Content/Factory.cpp:471
#, no-c-format
msgid "Speed dolphin"
msgstr "Hitrost dolfinja"

#: src/InfoBoxes/Content/Factory.cpp:473
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Instantaneous MacCready speed-to-fly, making use of netto vario calculations"
" to determine dolphin cruise speed on the glider's current track. In cruise "
"flight mode, this speed-to-fly is calculated for maintaining altitude. In "
"final glide mode, this speed-to-fly is calculated for descent. In climb "
"mode, this switches to the speed for minimum sink at the current load factor"
" (if an accelerometer is connected). When Block mode speed-to-fly is "
"selected, this InfoBox displays the MacCready speed."
msgstr ""
"Srednji hitrost dolfinja MacCready, ki uporablja izračune netto varija za "
"odrejanje dolfinjske hitrosti na trenutni poti letala. V režimu leta je ta "
"hitrost dolfinja za ohranjanje višine. V režimu končnega drsa je ta hitrost "
"dolfinja za opustoščanje. V režimu poniščevanja se pretvori v hitrost za "
"minimum sink na trenutnem faktorju nabočnosti (če je povezan akcelerometer)."
" Ko je izbrana hitrost dolfinja bloka, prikazuje se MacCready hitrost."

#: src/InfoBoxes/Content/Factory.cpp:479
#, no-c-format
msgid "Netto vario"
msgstr "Neto variometer"

#: src/InfoBoxes/Content/Factory.cpp:480
#, no-c-format
msgid "Netto"
msgstr "Netno"

#: src/InfoBoxes/Content/Factory.cpp:481
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Instantaneous vertical speed of air-mass, equal to vario value less the "
"glider's estimated sink rate. Best used if airspeed, accelerometers and "
"vario are connected, otherwise calculations are based on GPS measurements "
"and wind estimates."
msgstr ""
"Srednji vertikalni hitrost zraka, enak razliki med varijom in oceno "
"poniščevanja letala. Najbolje uporabljeno, če so povezani hitri variometer, "
"hitrosti vzduha in akcelerometeri, drugače so izračuni založeni na merjenjih"
" GPS-a in ocenah vetra."

#: src/InfoBoxes/Content/Factory.cpp:487
#, no-c-format
msgid "Task arrival time"
msgstr "Čas prihodka naloge"

#: src/InfoBoxes/Content/Factory.cpp:488
#, no-c-format
msgid "Fin ETA"
msgstr "Konečna ETA"

#: src/InfoBoxes/Content/Factory.cpp:489
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Estimated arrival local time at task completion, assuming performance of "
"ideal MacCready cruise/climb cycle."
msgstr ""
"Ocena lokalne časa prihodka na koncu nalogo, predpostavljeno idealno "
"MacCready ciklus leta/poniščevanja."

#: src/InfoBoxes/Content/Factory.cpp:495
#, no-c-format
msgid "Next arrival time"
msgstr "Naslednji čas prihodka"

#: src/InfoBoxes/Content/Factory.cpp:496
#, no-c-format
msgid "WP ETA"
msgstr "TOČKA POTI ETA"

#: src/InfoBoxes/Content/Factory.cpp:497
