"convection height and cloud base in conjunction with outside air temperature"
" and relative humidity probe. (Touch-screen/PC only) Pressing the up/down "
"cursor keys adjusts this forecast temperature."
msgstr ""
"Prognozirana temperatura podloge na domačem letališču, uporabljena za oceno "
"višine konvekcije in podnebi v zvezi s zunanjim atmosferskim temperaturem in"
" umikom relativne vlage. (Prestavljeno/PC leto) Pritisnite gumbe za "
"povečanje ali zmanjšanje, da se spremeni ta prognozirana temperatura."

#: src/InfoBoxes/Content/Factory.cpp:536
#, no-c-format
msgid "AAT distance around target"
