msgid "GR Avg"
msgstr "GR Prosek"

#: src/InfoBoxes/Content/Factory.cpp:699
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Distance flown during the configured averaging period divided by the "
"altitude lost during that period. Negative values are shown as ^^^ and "
"indicate climbing cruise (height gain). For GR >200, the value is shown as "
"+++. You can configure the averaging period in the system setup (suggested: "
"60, 90 or 120s). Lower values will be closer to GR Inst, and higher values "
"will be closer to GR Cruise. Note: The distance is not the straight line "
"between your previous and current positions; it is the actual path distance "
"flown (including zigzags). This value is not calculated while circling."
msgstr ""
"Razdalja leta v postavljeno srednjo obdobje deljena z izgubljenimi višinami "
"v tem istem obdobju. Negativne vrednosti so prikazane kot ^^^ in pomenijo "
"klimanjeno kroženje (višinsko zmago). Če je GR > 200, ta vrednost je "
"prikazana kot +++. Možno je nastaviti srednjo obdobje v sistemskih "
"nastavitvah (pogostek: 60, 90 ali 120s). Nizke vrednosti so bližje GR Inst, "
"a viške vrednosti so bližje GR Cruise. Opomba: Razdalja ni pravila povezana "
"s prejšnjim in trenutnim položajem; je dejanska razdalja leta (vključno z "
"zigažagami). Ta vrednost se ne izračuna, ko se kroži."

